    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Dark brown or black non-living organic substance derived from microbial decomposition of plant and animal substances on the surface of the earth. Living plants derive nutrients from the forms created by this decomposition.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
